fields.name: Shark Attack
fields.description: Swim through the ocean as a Great White shark. Eat as many fish as you can to become the biggest shark in the ocean! First shark to grow to 100ft wins!

fields.name: Falcon Five
fields.description: You and four other friends will fly through the sky as a Perigrine Falcons. Take down as many prey as possible within 10 minutes! The Falcon with the most take downs at the end of the round wins!
